code:
 (* Write a  function to find the minimum difference between any two elements in a given array. https://www.geeksforgeeks.org/find-minimum-difference-pair/ *)
let rec min_diff_pair arr =
  match arr with
  | [] -> raise Not_found
  | x :: xs ->
      let x_min = min_diff_pair xs in
      let x_max = min_diff_pair (xs - x) in
      let x_diff = x_max - x_min in
      if x_diff < 0 then x_min else x_max
in
let rec min_diff_pair_opt arr =
  match arr with
  | [] -> None
  | x :: xs ->
      let x_min = min_diff_pair_opt xs in
      let x_max = min_diff_pair_opt (xs - x) in
      let x_diff = x_max - x_min in
      if x_diff < 0 then x_min else x_max
in
let rec min_diff_pair_opt_opt arr =
  match arr with

 (* Write a  function to find the minimum difference between any two elements in a given array. https://www.geeksforgeeks.org/find-minimum-difference-pair/ *)
let rec min_diff_pair arr =
  match arr with
  | [] -> raise Not_found
  | x :: xs ->
      let x_min = min_diff_pair xs in
      let x_max = min_diff_pair (xs - x) in
      let x_diff = x_max - x_min in
      if x_diff < 0 then x_min else x_max
in
let rec min_diff_pair_opt arr =
  match arr with
  | [] -> None
  | x :: xs ->
      let x_min = min_diff_pair_opt xs in
      let x_max = min_diff_pair_opt (xs - x) in
      let x_diff = x_max - x_min in
      if x_diff < 0 then x_min else x_max
in
let rec min_diff_pair_opt_opt arr =
  match arr with
  | [] -> None
  | x :: xs ->
      let x_min = min_diff_pair_opt_opt xs in
      let x_max = min_diff

  match arr with
  | [] -> raise Not_found
  | x :: xs ->
      let x_min = min_diff_pair xs in
      let x_max = min_diff_pair (xs - x) in
      let x_diff = x_max - x_min in
      if x_diff < 0 then x_min else x_max
in
let rec min_diff_pair_opt arr =
  match arr with
  | [] -> None
  | x :: xs ->
      let x_min = min_diff_pair_opt xs in
      let x_max = min_diff_pair_opt (xs - x) in
      let x_diff = x_max - x_min in
      if x_diff < 0 then x_min else x_max
in
let rec min_diff_pair_opt_opt arr =
  match arr with
  | [] -> None
  | x :: xs ->
      let x_min = min_diff_pair_opt_opt xs in
      let x_max = min_diff_pair_opt_opt (xs - x) in
      let x_diff = x_max - x_min in
      if x_diff < 0 then x_min else x_max
in
let rec min_diff_pair_opt_opt_opt arr =
  match arr with
  | [] -> None
  | x :: xs ->
      let x_min = min_diff_pair_opt_opt_opt xs in
      let x_max = min_diff_pair_opt_opt

 (* Write a  function to find the minimum difference between any two elements in a given array. https://www.geeksforgeeks.org/find-minimum-difference-pair/ *)
let rec min_diff_pair arr =
  match arr with
  | [] -> raise Not_found
  | x :: xs ->
      let x_min = min_diff_pair xs in
      let x_max = min_diff_pair (xs - x) in
      let x_diff = x_max - x_min in
      if x_diff < 0 then x_min else x_max
in
let rec min_diff_pair_opt arr =
  match arr with
  | [] -> None
  | x :: xs ->
      let x_min = min_diff_pair_opt xs in
      let x_max = min_diff_pair_opt (xs - x) in
      let x_diff = x_max - x_min in
      if x_diff < 0 then x_min else x_max
in
let rec min_diff_pair_opt_opt arr =
  match arr with
  | [] -> None
  | x :: xs ->
      let x_min = min_diff_pair_opt_opt xs in
      let x_max = min_diff_pair_opt_opt (xs - x) in
      let x_diff = x_max - x_min in
      if x_diff < 0 then x_min else x_max
in
let rec min_diff_pair_opt_opt_opt arr =
  match arr with
  | [] -> None
  | x :: xs ->
      let x_min = min_diff_pair_opt_opt_opt xs in
      let x_max = min_diff_pair_opt_opt_opt (xs - x) in
      let x_diff = x_max - x_min in
      if x_diff < 0 then x_min else x_max
in

  match arr with
  | [] -> None
  | x :: xs ->
      let x_min = min_diff_pair_opt_opt_opt_opt xs in
      let x_max = min_diff_pair_opt

 (* Write a  function to find the minimum difference between any two elements in a given array. https://www.geeksforgeeks.org/find-minimum-difference-pair/ *)
let rec min_diff_pair arr =
  match arr with
  | [] -> raise Not_found
  | x :: xs ->
      let x_min = min_diff_pair xs in
      let x_max = min_diff_pair (xs - x) in
      let x_diff = x_max - x_min in
      if x_diff < 0 then x_min else x_max
in
let rec min_diff_pair_opt arr =
  match arr with
  | [] -> None
  | x :: xs ->
      let x_min = min_diff_pair_opt xs in
      let x_max = min_diff_pair_opt (xs - x) in
      let x_diff = x_max - x_min in
      if x_diff < 0 then x_min else x_max
in
let rec min_diff_pair_opt_opt arr =
  match arr with
  | [] -> None
  | x :: xs ->
      let x_min = min_diff_pair_opt_opt xs in
      let x_max = min_diff_pair_opt_opt (xs - x) in
      let x_diff = x_max - x_min in
      if x_diff < 0 then x_min else x_max
in
let rec min_diff_pair_opt_opt_opt arr =
  match arr with
  | [] -> None
  | x :: xs ->
      let x_min = min_diff_pair_opt_opt_opt xs in
      let x_max = min_diff_pair_opt_opt_opt (xs - x) in
      let x_diff = x_max - x_min in
      if x_diff < 0 then x_min else x_max
in

      let x_min = min_diff_pair_opt_opt_opt_opt xs in
      let x_max = min_diff_pair_opt_opt_opt_opt (xs - x) in
